cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is about video object segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper discusses various refinements to a propagation-based method, which involves using machine learning techniques such as neural networks (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the impact of these refinements on the final model performance, which involves measuring metrics such as accuracy and speed (cs.MM). Finally, the paper mentions using space-time memory networks, which are a type of recurrent neural network (cs.NE).
